Package edu.umn.biomedicus.tnt

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KnownWordsDataStore  
    WordProbabilityModel
    Interface for word probability models.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KnownWordProbabilityModel
    Statistical model used for known words in the TnT tagger. It gives the probability that a word will occur given a part of speech tag and capitalization. It stores these probabilities in a Map from WordPosCap objects to their double probabilities between 0.0 and 1.0. Stores candidates PartOfSpeech values for words for speed, even though this data is recoverable from the probabilities map.
    SuffixWordProbabilityModel
    Statistical model used for determining the probability of words given the part of speech and capitalization. Is based off a suffix method described in
    TnTTrainerProcessor
    Trains the TnT model using the tagged parts of speech in all documents.
    TntModel  
    TntModelTrainer
    Trains a model for the TnT part of speech tagger.
    TntPosTagger
    Part of speech tagger implementation for the TnT algorithm.
    WordCapAdapter  
    WordCapFilter
    Used to filter certain words from entering the statistics model
